modName: Camera INI Tweaks for Wrye Bash
summary: Camera INI Tweaks for Wrye Bash is a collection of tweaks that improve the first person camera experience, easily installable and configurable in wrye bash.  Just install with bash and the tweaks will show up in your ini edits tab :D
